00:30:52.780 --> 00:30:54.370
I could have...

00:30:54.370 --> 00:31:00.260
&gt;&gt;male speaker 2: The charge is arbitrary,
the numbers arbitrary [unintelligible]

00:31:00.260 --> 00:31:01.260
&gt;&gt;Allen: Yeah.

00:31:01.260 --> 00:31:02.610
Right, so in that case,
