that postulated a different

00:31:06.590 --> 00:31:08.770
set of entities.

00:31:08.770 --> 00:31:11.330
More different
than just positive and negative charge.

00:31:11.330 --> 00:31:15.550
And that other physics might be
just as good as what we currently call physics.

00:31:15.550 --> 00:31:20.660
It's not easy to make one up as a good example
