00:31:24.390 --> 00:31:26.550
realism and instrumentalism.

00:31:26.550 --> 00:31:30.780
the other one is reductionism and holism.

00:31:30.780 --> 00:31:33.000
I'm torn about how far to get into that one.

00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:36.320
Hofstadter talks about this in Gödel, Escher
