00:52:15.519 --> 00:52:20.359
thing about the droplets moving
at these discrete velocities, and that there's

00:52:20.359 --> 00:52:21.859
a quantized charge.

00:52:21.859 --> 00:52:26.859
And so, one can assign quantification of that,
