00:57:42.860 --> 00:57:46.280
[quiet laughter]
So I think the challenge then for theory choice

00:57:46.280 --> 00:57:50.320
is to distinguish between what are the preferences
we have,

00:57:50.320 --> 00:57:56.280
just because that's how we are, versus preferences
that we can justify in terms of properties

00:57:56.280 --> 00:57:58.030
such as being truth tropic.

00:57:58.030 --> 00:58:02.150
You know, I think this is more likely to lead
toward more truth,

00:58:02.150 --> 00:58:05.100
you know, I think this theory is better than
that one,

00:58:05.100 --> 00:58:08.310
not just because my monkey brain tells me
that it's better,

00:58:08.310 --> 00:58:11.869
but because I've got a justified reason to
believe that it's

00:58:11.869 --> 00:58:16.109
more likely to lead to, lead toward a truth,
be good for prediction,

00:58:16.109 --> 00:58:18.410
whatever the other characteristics are that
we have for a model.

00:58:18.410 --> 00:58:19.410
